                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": 276,
                              "content": "P0 (blocker):\n→ Auth + Onboarding iOS\n→ Today Cockpit + Training\n→ Shell Web + Dashboard\n\nP1 (S1 must-have):\n→ Nutrition iOS + Web NutOps\n→ Progress iOS + Analytics Web\n→ AI Coach iOS + AI Insights Web\n\nP2 (S2 backlog):\n→ Exercise substitution\n→ Video player captions\n→ Admin RBAC full\n→ Audit trail export\n→ Billing integration",
                              "fontFamily": "Manrope",
                              "fontSize": 11,
                              "fontWeight": "500"
